Google Dorking Report 
Google Dork use: 
1) Using intitle:atomic habits type:pdf 
By using this command on the browser, we can see all sites that offer a pdf downloa of the 
book. 
• https://archive.org/details/atomic-habits-pdfdrive 
• https://sistem42.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Atomic-Habits-James-Clear.pdf 
